'''Hyperspace Webcam''' was a feature on the ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|Hyperspace]] fan club website. It was a live-action webcam on-set during the production of [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. The webcam image updated online every twenty seconds. Several selections of webcam images were compiled in the [[Hyperspace Webcam Movies]].

